Path: godot/classes/class_foldablecontainer.rst
Summary: This chunk describes the `folding_changed` signal and the `TitlePosition` enumeration, including its constants `POSITION_TOP` and `POSITION_BOTTOM`.

Signal: folding_changed(is_folded: bool)
Emitted when the container is folded/expanded.

Enumerations
enum TitlePosition:
    POSITION_TOP = 0: Makes the title appear at the top of the container.
    POSITION_BOTTOM = 1: Makes the title appear at the bottom of the container. Also makes all StyleBoxes flipped vertically.
